Rule Engine
Implemented as independent modules:
• Duplicate Detection
• Threshold Violation
• Round Number Detection
• Debit/Credit Validation
• Vendor-Account Pairing
• Split Payment Detection
• Weekend/Holiday Transactions
• Missing Approval
• Inactive Vendor
• Benford's Law Analysis
Risk Scoring
Each rule contributes weighted points to calculate an overall risk score.
Example:
Duplicate = 40
Threshold = 30
Vendor = 15
Weekend = 10
Round Number = 5
Total = 100 (Critical Risk)
