Complete Workflow
1. User logs in.
2. Dashboard displays KPIs.
3. Auditor filters ledger.
4. Transaction selected.
5. Rule engine evaluates anomalies.
6. Risk score calculated.
7. RAG retrieves policy clauses and similar cases.
8. Claude generates structured audit note.
9. Auditor reviews and edits.
10. Manager approves.
11. Report archived with immutable audit log.
